# ImageUploader

`TxImageUploader` is a controlled image picker. It opens the native file input, creates local object URLs for selected images, renders preview tiles, and revokes owned object URLs when removed or unmounted.

Reviewed against `packages/tuffex/packages/components/src/image-uploader/src/types.ts`, `TxImageUploader.vue`, and `image-uploader.test.ts`.

